{"tid":2375322,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[狗屋狗車點解唔裝] 張宇人倡教室安裝閉路電視集中攝錄教師監察教學情況","createTime":"2021-01-22T02:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T07:42:08.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"96c85918e8a06544340abf3d023eefbe39de4cb9","tid":2375322,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:53:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571763-20210122.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571763-20210122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=ddda3c63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571763-20210122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=058f088c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571763-20210122.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自由黨議員張宇人認為，於課室安裝閉路電視時，應只集中攝錄教師，相信既有助監察教學情況，亦可以在教師受誣衊時，閉路電視可以還教師清白，不會「口同鼻拗」，而學生因病休假時，也可以觀看錄影片段，重溫課堂。他舉例說，目前不少補習社會都有錄影課堂，又指他於60年代在美國留學時，亦可翻看課堂片段<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">點解少數派保蝗狗唔支持狗屋狗車全部裝cam?</span>"},{"pid":"8b7422eea7de30fc30e1fa65776644969f9f5cdf","tid":2375322,"uid":30084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"今時今日重係到問點解對家唔乜乜乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為你地唔撚敢擺工囉 人地有權做乜撚都得喇<br />\n你地淆底唔敢反抗 咪硬食囉 食喇香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e555660b895d1cd8c3a046e351a5044b634c93","tid":2375322,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:55:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">亦可以在教師受誣衊時，閉路電視可以還教師清白，不會「口同鼻拗」</span></blockquote>要屈你個陣可以話某個時段，部機壞咗錄唔到，總之你有講過啦，釘牌，close file"},{"pid":"84934989287da7dbfbf9cfd3d9a9c913c8b73009","tid":2375322,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:42:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">點解少數派保蝗狗唔支持狗屋狗車全部裝cam?</span>"}]}